igure out the rest.Also, speed up the combat speed to max in the settings, yes it looks a little silly but so much better.Might seem i have more negatives than positives, but i've managed 60 hours in barely over a week and seeing i work and  do other stuff, this is pretty much all i've been playing.Highly enjoyable and worth a shot."
