76561198063851029,Recommended,232050,33162695,Posted: 2 July,all,DarkH,"Eador Masters of the Broken World is a TSRPG (Turn-base Strategy Role Playing Game), we are a God that willingly decided to experience a mortals life and then ascended once again but this time with no memory of our past immortal life.With that said the premise is quite open to whatever story you want yourself to experience, there are consequences for whatever behaviour you display while managing your Heros in the Mortal plane or even in the Astral Plane where you can befriend or not other Gods or Demi-Gods.One thing i like in this game is how long the game is, eventhough it's quite long for most people i find it to be fitting considering we are a God who witnesses several Mortal lives, in short eternity, to actually decide what we truly want to do."
